Title:
- Fixed a bug where the player would be out of range in attacks.ts.
- Changed TheEntity's attack time from 2 to 10 to 4 to 10.
- Made players' speed be reset when they leave wind area (so they do not have a speed bost.)
- Removed music from repository for copyright issues.
- Modified music handler and helper (because of the above change).
- Renamed and changed directory for all music.
- Renamed BP to NG1_BP and RP to NG1_RP.